Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  约定…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我会遵守的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协助「日本行政特区」？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此  也无法消除的你所犯下的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:22.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白  暂时撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.21,0:02:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑之骑士团打算再次潜入海底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去追捕Vincent吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的C.C.搜索行动到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是被抓住了  连我也要被…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说要加入行政特区
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.11,0:02:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底在打什么主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是Zero的判断  对不起我们日本人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤堂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:02:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟让新婚妻子等那么久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐耶殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到您如往常一样精神  我就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero大人才是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是让人吃惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然说要加入日本特区
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.41,0:03:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说啦  那是假装接受邀请  趁机击溃布列塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗  不停的战斗  那又能带来什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着  该不是要跟他们妥协吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说你有不用战斗就能解决问题的方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算从布列塔尼亚内部变革吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是为了独立而…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样才算日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Area 11的各位民众
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是布列塔尼亚政府广播
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  日本特区
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这样  一会儿就胆怯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是一个杀戮公主吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  Zero也说要参加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强制劳动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易从Eleven转成了名誉布列塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要变回日本人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那些没工作的人才会去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本行政特区的参加者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前为止似乎还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero那边也是音信全无
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是为了调解黑之骑士团内部的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要花上一些功夫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然这只是政厅相关人员的推测而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次请一定要按这边的原稿来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为总督…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总督并非皇帝陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充其量  您只是作为皇帝陛下的代理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮助管理各殖民区
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次日本特区的事虽然已经妥善处理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过今后的事情应该先跟大家商讨一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休学？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为以后会越来越忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本特区啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那庭院计划怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.27,0:04:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情告一段落后还会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  朱雀君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于华莲的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能想点办法帮她一把吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:05:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  不是有「司法交易」之类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也懂得世界需要和平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但亲人朋友也是很重要的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能跟总督什么的商量一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像上次那样  让我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？  鲁路跟总督说过话？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟幼女公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是啦  是在欢迎会那晚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是认错人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈话都是糊里糊涂的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行哎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修  你真的丧失记忆了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是已经恢复记忆  希望你能回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要杀死尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该还有其他方法才对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奸贼  枢木朱雀！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.67,0:05:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木卿  没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对内心深处渴求死之惩罚的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:05:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施予「活下去」的Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我就知道会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经让篠崎咲世子前往了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  做得好  迪特哈尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然十分优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卓越非凡  举世无双的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您的夸奖  光荣之极
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后的安排也跟计划的一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  虽然战术目标改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战略目的还是没变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有忘记我们的约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  我要守护这所学校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护你的容身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及我们的日常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我否定布列塔尼亚那虚伪的支配
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有要守护的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才会帮助哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的事被暴露了  这个学园就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  而且  V.V.…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  作为叛徒的我也会完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我也完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是同一命运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社团活动拖太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事  Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样迟早会穿帮的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想见扇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第五阶段确认到初始现象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:23.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\fad(200,100)\pos(560,343)}神圣布列塔尼亚帝国\N达拉斯研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:25.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒计时  20 19…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了  妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡隆先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连修奈泽尔殿下也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候从EU那边回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经成功跟法国议和了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样还不如  一直进攻下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过多的胜利只会酝酿今后的败北
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都会探求希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜利其实就是践踏他人的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌我都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大家肯定都有自己的追求
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是  朱雀的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来它很喜欢你啊  阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的服装？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修行的时候都是穿这身衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很怀念吗  「日本」？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢…确实也有过美好的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木卿  您在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有文件需要您签名确认
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对袭击枢木卿的Eleven执行死刑的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得圆桌骑士以上级别的认可  即可行刑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验仍在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会浪费殿下当时对我的眷顾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色暴动的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  罗伊德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连米蕾也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:09.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我杀了Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要替尤菲米娅殿下报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然从最初的试作品就一直失败
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  再给我点时间的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是为尤菲而行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然她以不幸的形式在史册中留下污名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我相信她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.36,0:09:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯内莉亚  娜娜莉  卡隆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有朱雀君  他们都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你也相信着尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因此我也相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  枢木卿…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是圆桌骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  没问题  那我先告退了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:09:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:09:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是  「受虐狂」？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知被怨恨还要请缨到Area 11来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Numbers」的英雄  出卖日本的人  Zero的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是被告席
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒和怨恨会毁掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不再奢求别人的理解什么的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为曾经有过一个能理解我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我原本就是个罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等的联络终于来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我在这里真的没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想见见Zero对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为其他机密设备都为特区做准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也不是该对外公布的谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此  那个装扮是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  今后会注意的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  有三名圆桌骑士在此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.42,0:11:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  总督好像不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是事务层面的谈话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  有件事想问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟之前的Zero是同一个人吗  还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero的真伪不在于他的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是以其行动作为判断的依据
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  真有哲理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑之骑士团的意见统一了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入日本特区可不是随便说说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会动员100万人前去参加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100万？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:34.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  有个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你们能放我一条生路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.06,0:11:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此  你们也有自己的苦衷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把Zero放逐国外这样的处分如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑之骑士团呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是打算舍弃掉的吧  你只会自顾自己的命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个对话要是曝光了  恐怕会被组织处以极刑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以为了不被杀掉才选择密谈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民区特殊法例12条第8项
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据这条法规
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总督权限内是可以执行放逐国外的处分的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗麦尔女士  你打算放走Zero吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是陈述司法解释而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在仪式上发表也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你们而言…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首领逃走了  Area 11的恐怖分子也只能半途而废了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  把犯罪者…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与事务人员协议的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:38.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为将Zero放逐国外的处罚是妥当的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.93,0:12:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能凭我一己之见就赦免他所有的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写对了吗  尤菲姐姐的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.49,0:12:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲  我们会继承你的遗志
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:13:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为你创造一个和平温馨的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来除我们以外还有其他人在悼念尤菲的死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除我们以外还有其他人啊  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一切已经就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没有任何留恋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是静冈贫民区  日本行政特区的预定地点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\fad(200,500)\pos(550,353)}静冈贫民区
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仪式马上就要开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此处已经聚集了大量的Eleven
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:37.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有超过100万人参加
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份确认将放到仪式之后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时  这动员人数
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明是Zero的话  对Eleven而言依然极具分量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那个Zero却打算背叛Eleven
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会引发暴动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候  我们就有肃清他们的大义名分了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我们可不能先出手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:13:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…千草？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇要  真的来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  要你特地来接我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  倒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底只是个代理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的总领事定下来后只能回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这也是个良机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.33,0:14:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  黑之骑士团…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的申请是为了以后作准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻大人  果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意  再撑一阵就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位日本民众  欢迎来到日本行政特区
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:44.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么多人前来  我感到无比欣慰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了崭新的历史  请务必借我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔福特卿  以您目前的身体状况…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是尤菲米娅殿下的夙愿  日本特区啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  Zero还未现身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个明哲保身的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要安全得以保障就会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么在仪式开始之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我传达我们与Zero达成的协议
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为帝国臣民  对加入日本行政特区的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给予特赦  罪减一等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三级以下的罪犯将缓刑处理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  杀害卡纳雷斯前总督等罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为主谋者的责任难以饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据殖民区特别法规12条第8项
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅将Zero逐出国境作为惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧？只有Zero？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就是只让他一个人逃走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  布列塔尼亚的诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宽大处置让在下惶愧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若引发暴动的话就是个处决危险分子的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然罗麦尔女士是这样叮嘱过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现身吧  Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.15,0:15:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将保证你安全放逐国外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无需借助他人之力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:15:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你  枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话问你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的日本人  所谓的民族是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:06.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,语言吗  土地吗  血统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自觉  规范  矜持
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说只要有心灵这个文化之根源
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论身在何处  都是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟你一个人逃走有何关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然演变成那样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总督
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军  准备镇压
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.51,0:16:46.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着  对方还没有动手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实  也许是Zero的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  事到如今Zero要是再不露面的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？一开始就在会场内了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Zero  Zero确实出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这一手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反利用压倒性的战斗力差距
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将100万人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有Zero啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉娜娜莉新总督的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻接受驱逐出境的处罚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论身处何地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我们保持这份「心灵」  我们就是日本人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:30.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  去我们的新天地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位Zero  一起去新天地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起被放逐到国外去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.33,0:17:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是Zero啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我们都是Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱逐出境了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算合法逃走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设计让他们暴动的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟适得其反了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们没有同时移动100万人的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,港湾管理室发来报告
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,港湾？难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:18:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中华联邦申请的海冰船？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,申请者已经在仪式开始前就离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在确认上花费了点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要坐那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  是冰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会融化掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘海冰船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有特制的隔热聚合物和超珀尔帖致冷膜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}（珀尔帖  (Peltier)：一种利用温差电效应制成的电导热材料）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以确保冰块万无一失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在关键是Zero  找出真正的Zero来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找出真身未免…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变成怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero不是偶像而是象征
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  他已自化为一种符号了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘掉面具  Eleven的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  布列塔婆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是来战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…扇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在确认  罗麦尔女士留在现场指挥了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说交给她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:18:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀也在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木卿  与其放走100万劳动力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如杀一儆百
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero  命令大家摘掉面具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去  又会有很多人死去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.19,0:19:16.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀君  既然没有人知道zero的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根本毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是叛乱吧  快下攻击命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  这是采取战斗以外的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责人可是你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放过Zero不就等于原谅他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括这100万人也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没了黑之骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Area 11就能获得和平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用玷污娜娜莉的双手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这是卑鄙的暗算
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下令吧  放走Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该下令  攻击Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧  Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  不能凭我一己之见就将罪行…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲和娜娜莉都打算宽恕的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方可是Zero啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero被判驱逐出境
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.47,0:20:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,违背约定的话  其他国民也不会再相信我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国民？你指那些Eleven？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你是「Numbers」出身…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟「Number」没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  留下不赞成国策的人又有何用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.33,0:20:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这100万人侮辱了布列塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是这种危险分子  才更应该放逐不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答应我  Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要拯救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.43,0:20:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木朱雀  反倒是你能拯救他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救留在Area 11的日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正是为此而加入军队的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你的诺言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.19,0:20:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗  所有的Zero啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木卿发表宣言了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放逐危险分子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:21:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们的障碍已经消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻出发  去自由之地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧  趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再…再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布列塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  眼睁睁看着这么多危险分子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星刻大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Area 11的事似乎进展得很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算登上我们的舞台了吗  Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.88,0:21:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀君所救的这100万人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.82,0:21:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不会感谢他的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.95,0:21:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点他早就知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.58,0:21:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是相信我不会下令开枪才制定的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero很了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为是最棘手的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这也是因为理解娜娜莉  才能做出这样的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:57.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  暂且先感谢你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.18,0:21:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.20,0:22:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后  别忘了你的承诺


